title: Virginia Tech takes down North Carolina 87-80 in overtime - VT hokiesports.com
content: Virginia Tech takes down North Carolina 87-80 in overtime  VT hokiesports.com
description: Emily Lytle put the Virginia Tech women's basketball team ahead for good with 2:30 to go the extra period to give the Hokies an 87-80 win over the North Carolina Tar Heels at Greensboro Coliseum Complex Friday.
